            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~odysseus_complex" class="author" title="author name and user ID">odysseus_complex (79966) </a> | about 10 months ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4493645&cid=45541653">(#45541653)</a></h4>
