            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~X-Ray+Artist" class="author" title="author name and user ID">X-Ray Artist (1784416) </a> | about 10 months ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4493645&cid=45541779">(#45541779)</a></h4>
